<dd class='comment-body' id='Blog1_cmt-7966835683254790018'>
<p>
fellow game developer here...<br /><br />Have you ever used PowerLoom?<br /><br />To implement PowerLoom we developed a new programming language called STELLA, which is a Strongly Typed, Lisp-like LAnguage that can be translated into Lisp, C++ and Java. PowerLoom is written in STELLA and therefore available in Common-Lisp, C++ and Java versions.
</p>
</dd>
