<h2>About Me</h2>
<div class='widget-content'>
<a href='http://www.blogger.com/profile/16229508667482062327'><img alt='My Photo' class='profile-img' height='63' src='http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_2P1ZGKDPDM0/TH-bhLwfvlI/AAAAAAAABAE/3X2QogezSUM/S220/profile-blur.jpg' width='80'/></a>
<dl class='profile-datablock'>
<dt class='profile-data'>Andreas Fredriksson</dt>
<dd class='profile-textblock'>Software Engineer at EA DICE. Past projects include four of the Battlefield games. I'm currently working on the Frostbite game engine.

I'm into portability, debugging and writing tools such as compilers and code generators.</dd>
</dl>
